{"_id":"64142f31f0cf00832960c7d5","area_name":"Pillar Wall","shortCode":"","climbs":[{"_id":"eluARicGQPWEVilE8o5xzQ==","name":"Business Time","type":{"trad":false,"sport":false,"bouldering":false,"alpine":false,"snow":false,"ice":true,"mixed":false,"aid":false,"tr":false},"gradeContext":"US","fa":"Greg Hughes and party, March 2020","length":14,"content":{"description":"\nOften dangling fat pillar at the south end of Pillar Wall. A spill is going to get your socks wet. \n\n\n\n30 seconds North of Mainstreet.\n\nStandard Ice Rack"},"metadata":{"left_right_index":-1,"areaRef":"zW0JzC+QXPWemdVRNWiO0w==","lnglat":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[-64.41852,45.44989]}},"createdBy":"IKxcZIprW86z0qjua5527Q==","_change":{"user":"IKxcZIprW86z0qjua5527Q==","historyId":"64142f34f0cf00832960c7e3","operation":"updateClimb","seq":0},"updatedAt":"2023-03-17T09:13:24.758Z"},{"_id":"LZbOk3g6QSinrrRJ+/E/kA==","name":"French Connection","type":{"trad":false,"sport":false,"bouldering":false,"alpine":false,"snow":false,"ice":true,"mixed":false,"aid":false,"tr":true},"gradeContext":"US","fa":"Dave MacFadden, Matthew Peck","length":18,"content":{"description":"\nThe Ice ramp directly across from Vortex, this climb gives easy access to the East side of the Upper Gorge/Merger. \n\n\n\nDescend Vortex and climb out , or take your chances with a ford from the bottom of Mainstreet. \n\nStandard Ice Rack"},"metadata":{"left_right_index":-1,"areaRef":"zW0JzC+QXPWemdVRNWiO0w==","lnglat":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[-64.41852,45.44989]}},"createdBy":"IKxcZIprW86z0qjua5527Q==","_change":{"user":"IKxcZIprW86z0qjua5527Q==","historyId":"64142f35f0cf00832960c7ed","operation":"updateClimb","seq":0},"updatedAt":"2023-03-17T09:13:25.296Z"},{"_id":"YA9U6OZXTC2iph9o4x3R0A==","name":"Haiku","type":{"trad":false,"sport":false,"bouldering":false,"alpine":false,"snow":false,"ice":true,"mixed":false,"aid":false,"tr":true},"gradeContext":"US","fa":"Matthew Peck, Dave MacFadden '18","length":15,"content":{"descriptio